@startuml view_network_graph

' Component definitions
participant "Business User" as User
participant "NetworkGraphUI\n(detect_communities or\nproject_sna pages)" as NetworkGraphUI

' Sequence flow
User -> NetworkGraphUI: Navigate to network graph\n(from detect_communities or project_sna)
activate NetworkGraphUI

NetworkGraphUI -> NetworkGraphUI: Initialize network visualization\ncomponent
activate NetworkGraphUI
note right: Loads JavaScript libraries\nfor interactive graph rendering
deactivate NetworkGraphUI

NetworkGraphUI -> NetworkGraphUI: Render network data\n(nodes and edges)
activate NetworkGraphUI
note right: Displays nodes as circles\nEdges as connections\nCommunities with color coding
deactivate NetworkGraphUI

NetworkGraphUI --> User: Display interactive\nnetwork visualization
deactivate NetworkGraphUI

User -> NetworkGraphUI: Interact with graph\n(zoom, pan, select nodes)
activate NetworkGraphUI

NetworkGraphUI -> NetworkGraphUI: Update visualization\nbased on user interaction
activate NetworkGraphUI
deactivate NetworkGraphUI

NetworkGraphUI --> User: Updated graph view
deactivate NetworkGraphUI

alt community detection was run
    User -> NetworkGraphUI: View community clusters
    activate NetworkGraphUI
    
    NetworkGraphUI --> User: Display nodes colored\nby community membership
    deactivate NetworkGraphUI
end

@enduml
